channel.title: My silabsoft client wont work!
channel.description:
Hey
My silabclient isn't working. I go to [url=http://www.client.silabsoft.org]www.client.silabsoft.org[/url], I get no security warning to press Run on and it goes too [url=http://www.client.silabsoft.org/loaderror_download%20client.html]http://www.client.silabsoft.org/loaderror_download%20client.html[/url]
I have tried turning off all my firewalls, I have made it so I accept all cookies on my IE and I have no parental controls... obviously!
Anyone know how to help?
Thanks

item.title: My silabsoft client wont work!
item.dc:creator: @onexan onexan
item.description:
@onexan wrote:

Go to your windows folder ex: “C:\Windows” search for .silabclient_store_32 folder click right button on it and press delete
